[operator]<i> Good evening, Mr. Wright.</i>

44:42.930 --> 44:47.935
Hi. I'd like to make a phone call please,
to Stephanie Kapoor.

44:48.018 --> 44:50.896
The number is area code 3-8-0...

44:51.563 --> 44:53.107
5-5-5...

44:54.149 --> 44:56.777
0-1-8...

45:00.239 --> 45:04.368
[operator] <i>And the final digit?</i>
<i>Mr. Wright, are you there?</i>

45:06.286 --> 45:08.330
[speaking Spanish]

45:08.414 --> 45:11.834
If that's a booty call from one of
your exes because of that magazine...

45:13.502 --> 45:14.378
[Aaron] What?

45:15.254 --> 45:18.090
-Lorraine?
-Aaron. Can we talk?

45:18.632 --> 45:22.553
[stutters] Actually, right now
is not a good time at all, really.

45:22.636 --> 45:25.013
Come by the campaign office
first thing in the morning.

45:25.097 --> 45:26.932
And think about whether
you'd like to join the ticket

45:27.015 --> 45:28.809
as Kirkman's vice president.

45:39.570 --> 45:41.530
Penny, what are you still doing awake?

45:41.613 --> 45:43.157
I waited up for you.

45:44.032 --> 45:44.992
Pudding?

45:45.659 --> 45:47.035
Sure, why not?

45:49.246 --> 45:50.706
Well, thank you.

45:52.875 --> 45:54.376
How was North Carolina?

45:55.502 --> 45:59.006
North Carolina, well...
The fundraiser went late.

45:59.089 --> 46:00.632
Did you announce your new law?

46:02.342 --> 46:04.428
No. Not yet, sweetheart.

46:05.679 --> 46:06.555
Why?

46:10.225 --> 46:11.310
Just 'cause.

46:21.695 --> 46:24.156
Dr. Fein's security
is a little higher than yours.

46:24.239 --> 46:25.908
It's new from last year.

46:25.991 --> 46:28.076
His car was outside. He has to be here.

46:29.077 --> 46:30.704
All right, then maybe he's hurt.

46:31.455 --> 46:32.789
You know what? Step back.

46:32.873 --> 46:34.458
Or I could just, uh...

46:49.097 --> 46:51.141
Now I really wanna talk to your friend.

46:51.225 --> 46:52.559
[Eli] This makes no sense.

46:53.435 --> 46:55.771
Why would he take his entire lab
but leave his car?

46:55.854 --> 46:56.939
Well, he wouldn't.

46:58.148 --> 47:00.776
This entire place
has been scrubbed with bleach.

47:12.871 --> 47:14.289
Do you know where he could be?

47:15.123 --> 47:15.958
No.

47:38.981 --> 47:40.566
